com.android.volley

Class RequestTickle

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.android.volley.RequestTickle

  • public class RequestTickle
extends java.lang.Object
    A request tickle for single requests. Calling add(Request) will add the request to request tickle and start(), will give a NetworkResponse. The listeners in the request will also be notified.
